data.description: Charming home in the heart of Midway ISD offers an open floor plan with a large family room, breakfast area & kitchen with fabulous backyard. Wonderful kitchen with great layout, stove, microwave, dishwasher, granite counters, and eat at bar. Family room is well laid out with large living space, wood-burning fireplace that creates an additional cozy feel, tall ceilings, and beautiful flooring.  Excellent spaced bedrooms throughout with good closet space. Spacious primary suite with two walk-in closets, double vanity, standalone shower & garden tub. Additional features are crown molding, 2 car garage, laundry room, fenced backyard, sprinkler system, gutters, and great trees plus a covered patio that provides a relaxing retreat that looks out onto a private above-ground pool complete with deck. Excellent location, priced right, this adorable home in Midway ISD will not last long.
